tputs":[{"output_type":"stream","name":"stdout","text":["[[ 0.94446029  0.32862557]\n"," [-0.32862557  0.94446029]]\n","[0.7625315 0.0184779]\n"]}]},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":["Визуализируем этот результат"],"metadata":{"id":"Ik8vfKrC277C"}},{"cell_type":"code","source":["import seaborn as sns\n","import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n","\n","\n","def draw_vector(v0, v1, ax=None):\n","    ax = ax or plt.gca()\n","    arrowprops=dict(arrowstyle='->',\n","                    linewidth=2,\n","                    shrinkA=0,\n","                    shrinkB=0,\n","                    color='black')\n","    ax.annotate('', v1, v0, arrowprops=arrowprops)\n","\n","\n","plt.figure(figsize=(15,10))\n","plt.scatter(X[:, 0], X[:, 1], alpha=0.5, color=\"red\")\n","for length, vector in zip(pca.explained_variance_, pca.components_):\n","    v = vector * 3 * np.sqrt(length)\n","    draw_vector(pca.mean_, pca.mean_ + v)\n","plt.axis('equal');"],"metadata":{"colab":{"base_uri":"https://localhost:8080/","height":835},"id":"E3MzMnmJr_ye","executionInfo":{"status":"ok","timestamp":1763558385830,"user_tz":-180,"elapsed":206,"user":{"displayName":"Сергей Артамонов","userId":"01556864889479707561"}},"outputId":"1de966b9-7a8b-4324-be0e-bddc3f33ff81"},"execution_count":null,"outputs":[{"output_type":"display_data","data":{"text/plain":["<Figure size 1500x1000 with 1 Axes>"],"image/png":"\n"},"metadata":{}}]},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":["Полученные векторы представляют главные \"оси\" в данных, а длина вектора указывает на то, насколько \"важна\" эта ось для описания распределения данных. Точнее, это мера дисперсии (разброса) данных при проецировании на эту ось.\n","\n","Проекция каждой точки данных на главные оси является \"главными компонентами\" данных, отсюда и название метод главных компонент.\n","\n"],"metadata":{"id":"BaT0xlmEuBif"}},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":["Далее мы на примере увидим, как можно применять PCA для снижения размерности в данных."],"metadata":{"id":"VfZkFmk8tggt"}},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":["## Применение PCA для снижения размерности многомерных данных\n","\n","Как вам кажется, сильно ли упадет качество классификации, если мы снизим размерность признакового описания радикально, то есть, скажем, с нескольких десятков тысяч до, скажем, десяти?\n","\n","Ответ на этот вопрос неоднозначен, в случае разных задач, разных алгоритмов, разных датасетов все будет по-разному.\n","\n","Однако давайте убедимся, что в каких-то случаях такое сильное снижение размерности не приведет к абсолютной несостоятельности алгоритма.\n","\n","Для примера возьмем уже известный нам датасет с новостными статьями из sklearn."],"metadata":{"id":"TFu1SJdq30q_"}},{"cell_type":"code","source":["from sklearn import datasets\n","from sklearn.feature_extraction.text import TfidfVectorizer\n","from sklearn.svm import SVC\n","from sklearn.model_selection import train_test_split\n","import sklearn\n","import numpy as np\n","\n","newsgroups = datasets.fetch_20newsgroups(\n","                    subset='all',\n","                    categories=['alt.atheism', 'sci.space']\n","             )"],"metadata":{"id":"T2H0gy7zBb50"},"execution_count":null,"outputs":[]},{"cell_type":"code","source":["y = newsgroups.target\n","X_train, x_test, y_train, y_test = train_test_split(newsgroups.data, y, test_size=0.3)"],"metadata":{"id":"7ZwonMqsw12U"},"execution_count":null,"outputs":[]},{"cell_type":"code","source":["vectorizer = TfidfVectorizer()\n","X_train = vectorizer.fit_transform(X_train)\n","x_test = vectorizer.transform(x_test)\n","y = newsgroups.target"],"metadata":{"id":"OiW_C0d3Bb-X"},"execution_count":null,"outputs":[]},{"cell_type":"code","source":["X_train.shape"],"metadata":{"colab":{"base_uri":"https://localhost:8080/"},"id":"XjeaBZYT46h4","executionInfo":{"status":"ok","timestamp":1763558453388,"user_tz":-180,"elapsed":13,"user":{"displayName":"Сергей Артамонов","userId":"01556864889479707561"}},"outputId":"9bd059ed-ab93-4b3b-962b-29257a02ea02"},"execution_count":null,"outputs":[{"output_type":"execute_result","data":{"text/plain":["(1250, 24183)"]},"metadata":{},"execution_count":19}]},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":["Как мы видим, в датасете содержится около 30 000 признаков. Давайте сожмем их, скажем, до 10."],"metadata":{"id":"6_LifnFT5DoT"}},{"cell_type":"code","source":["from sklearn.decomposition import PCA\n","import xgboost as xgb\n","from sklearn.metrics import accuracy_score\n","\n","n_comp = 10\n","pca = PCA(n_components=n_comp)\n","X_tr = pca.fit_transform(X_train.toarray())\n","x_te = pca.transform(x_test.toarray())\n","\n","clf = xgb.XGBClassifier().fit(X_tr, y_train)"],"metadata":{"id":"9ghsv-l846kx"},"execution_count":null,"outputs":[]},{"cell_type":"code","source":["X_tr.shape"],"metadata":{"colab":{"base_uri":"https://localhost:8080/"},"id":"ZkN95TNgw4OS","executionInfo":{"status":"ok","timestamp":1763558490633,"user_tz":-180,"elapsed":13,"user":{"displayName":"Сергей Артамонов","userId":"01556864889479707561"}},"outputId":"d198650c-9868-487c-c28a-cfcda5d9b5dc"},"execution_count":null,"outputs":[{"output_type":"execute_result","data":{"text/plain":["(1250, 10)"]},"metadata":{},"execution_count":21}]},{"cell_type":"code","source":["clf.score(X_tr, y_train)"],"metadata":{"colab":{"base_uri":"https://localhost:8080/"},"id":"AcnSYTQ8GPjd","executionInfo":{"status":"ok","timestamp":1763558495746,"user_tz":-180,"elapsed":46,"user":{"displayName":"Сергей Артамонов","userId":"01556864889479707561"}},"outputId":"e13805ef-e0bd-4e43-a98f-00d18060c6a6"},"execution_count":null,"outputs":[{"output_type":"execute_result","data":{"text/plain":["1.0"]},"metadata":{},"execution_count":22}]},{"cell_type":"code","source":["acc = accuracy_score(clf.predict(x_te), y_test)\n","acc"],"metadata":{"colab":{"base_uri":"https://localhost:8080/"},"id":"ObWZAa4m46oM","executionInfo":{"status":"ok","timestamp":1763558498487,"user_tz":-180,"elapsed":35,"user":{"displayName":"Сергей Артамонов","userId":"015568648894797